customValues.infoDesc:
After defeating the entity in the Backrooms, Boyfriend clips again. This time he clips into a empty grass field with nothing in sight. He looks down to see his body is different and he has no idea what is going on. He looks up to see a creature that followed the same shape as his new body did. He meets the "Guardian".





Based on Petscop by Tony Domenico.
